###  http://www.semanticweb.org/kaik/ontologies/2026/3/ivd-high-risk-medical-devices-eu/MDRRiskClass
<http://www.semanticweb.org/kaik/ontologies/2026/3/ivd-high-risk-medical-devices-eu/MDRRiskClass> rdf:type owl:Class ;
