                                                                                                  rdfs:comment """Class I: Low Risk, Self-Declaration
Class IIa: Medium-Low Risk, NB Audit
Class IIb: Medium-High Risk, Comprehensive NB Audit
Class III: High Risk, Strictest NB and Design Audit"""@en ;
                                                                                                  rdfs:label "MDR risk classification"@en .


